room_title: Escape room "Dinner at the Manor" by Epic Escape Game in Denver
room_address: 611 N. Wilcox Street, Castle Rock, CO 80104
room_description: Mr. Stein, a science mogul, is hosting a benefit dinner at his mansion to help the families of several missing tourists. You have been invited to the event as personal guests of Mr. Stein. Upon arrival, the butler informs you that your host is running late and will join you in 1 hour, then locks the door behind you. Something seems eerily wrong about this situation.
